The New Blackstone Pizza Oven is Now for Sale - CookOut News Advertise Newsletter FAQ Contact Us Search CookOut News The business of outdoor cooking CookOut News The business of outdoor cooking Camp Stove Manufacturers Fuel Grill Manufacturers Guides Industry Mergers & Acquisitions Newsletters People Pizza Oven Manufacturers Popular Retailers Rumors Technology Uncategorized Advertise Newsletter FAQ Contact Us Search Linkedin Twitter Instagram Facebook Pinterest Home Grill Manufacturers The New Blackstone Pizza Oven is Now for Sale Grill Manufacturers Pizza Oven Manufacturers The New Blackstone Pizza Oven is Now for Sale January 6, Share Facebook Twitter Pinterest Linkedin ReddIt Email Copy URL New Blackstone Pizza Oven Well, that didn’t take Blackstone teased their long awaited pizza oven yesterday and then today, just a day later, they launched it for sale on their That’s not much of a tease Blackstone! Features and Specs Retail price of $999 ( check price ) – they run sales , cooking chamber A pizza stone above and one below that you launch the pizza onto The lower stone rotates so you don’t have to rotate the pizza with a peel while cooking Big enough for pizzas up to ″ Temperatures up to degrees Electronic ignition system Blackstone Pizza Oven Dimensions Overview There’s a lot to like about Blackstone’s new pizza It checks all the boxes in terms of construction and The rotating stone adds convenience to cooking a pizza and lessons the learning curve for - Advertisement - Having an electronic ignition also is a great feature, especially if you are cooking in windy or cold One of our biggest complaints on pizza ovens we tested are the manual ignitors that are difficult to Comes on a Cart Pizza oven companies have been releasing carts and tables recently, to solve the problem of where to put your pizza Blackstone’s comes on a cart, so that is a nice Right now they only sell it on the cart, but we’d imagine they’ll be sold separately in the Blackstone Pizza Oven on the Cart and on a Table Conclusion If you’re in the market for a ″ pizza oven, the Blackstone Pizza Oven is definitely worth It’s a little pricey at $999, compared to the beloved Ooni Koda at $599. Once you start including the cost of a cart though and the value of the features the Blackstone adds, it becomes harder to pass - Get news like this in your email every Saturday - always free, never spam -
